survey_response.review_text: I had gone for a dental checkup today… Dr Nupur checked my teeth and did a nice cleaning for my teeth which had lot of tartar accumulated in them . The process was smooth and quick … i felt very nice after the cleaning and it was a nice experience with the doctor ⭐️⭐️⭐️🌟⭐️
Doctor was very friendly and explained the treatment well.She starred with my root canal today which went on smoothly.
Very friendly atmosphere which is very important to me as I was always scared of dentists . Dr Nupur  ,gave me enough time to  overcome my fears , answering all my queries with full information .

Dr Nupur Jhunjhunwala is a very professional doctor.  I was very comfortable with her approach to my dental fillings. She is very meticulous and was able to understand my dental problems very well.
She was very thorough and gentle while doing my dental fillings.  She also explained to me very succinctly my other dental problems and how they need to be tackled.
All in all a very good experience with Dr Nupur Jhunjhunwala.
I would definitely visit her again and definitely recommend her to others who require dental treatment.

I was terribly worried about my appointment as to what is going to happen. I was nervous. I had a nagging toothache and was told by other dental surgeons that the tooth is moving and may need an extraction. Dr Nupur did my tooth’s scan and decided on an extraction. This was very well explained  to me and I was now more relaxed and settled. While on the chair before I realised much my affected tooth was out - no pain no bleeding and I was there talking to the Doctor- ALL DONE so very well and me back to normal virtually instantly / 🙏🙏
Well done Dr Jhunjhunwala
The whole process was smooth and the check up went great as well. Would recommend her to everyone I know
